Model statistics function
You will use this function to calculate \(Adj. R^2\), AIC, and BIC in the cross validation.

calc_model_stats &lt;- function(x) {
  glance(extract_fit_parsnip(x)) |&gt;
    select(adj.r.squared, AIC, BIC)
}

